GameObject
Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
  GameObject.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
MovableObject, StaticObject
public class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object

Parent class to every object present in the game. Defines fundamental attributes present in every object that is rendered on the game grid. Namely, position on the grid, visibility, the image object associated, and the dimensions of the object.
